### Enrichment
GenCAD published as arXiv paper 2409.16294, accepted at OpenReview. Follow-up GenCAD-Self-Repairing (arXiv 2505.23287) addresses ~10% infeasible design rate with a diffusion guidance and self-repairing pipeline. SOTA in unconditional and conditional CAD generation. Project page: gencad.github.io.

